T1  - Marks of Distinction: Framing and Audience Appreciation in the Context of Investment Advice
AU  - Giorgi, Simona
AU  - Weber, Klaus
Y1  - 2015/06/01
PY  - 2015
DA  - 2015/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1177/0001839215571125
